- Constructor accepts `TextImagePipelineConstructorArgs` (expects both tokenizer and processor)
- `_call` method takes images (single or batch) and optional generate_kwargs
- Supports batched processing via `Array.isArray(images)` check
- Uses `prepareImages()` to process input images
- Uses `this.processor()` to get pixel values
- Iterates over each batch, adjusting dims to prepend batch dimension
- Calls `this.model.generate()` with pixel values
